  "description": "Producer gas generation from biomass via shaft gasifier: partial combustion produces CO+H₂+N₂ mixture (~5-6 MJ/m³). Gas cleaning via water scrubbing, sawdust filter, cyclone. Can power internal combustion engines directly. Powered vehicles during WWII fuel shortages. Bridge technology before natural gas infrastructure.",
